00:59:23,685 --> 00:59:24,602
Apa maksud awak?

908
00:59:25,812 --> 00:59:28,731
Awak benar-benar fikir
dia pengerusi Syarikat Babel?

909
00:59:30,149 --> 00:59:31,943
