913
00:59:39,492 --> 00:59:42,829
- Apa lagi masalahnya?
- Tiada apa-apa.

914
00:59:43,746 --> 00:59:45,248
Aduhai.

915
00:59:49,544 --> 00:59:51,921
- Tak guna.
- Kenapa?

916
00:59:53,423 --> 00:59:54,882
Guli ajaib saya.

917
00:59:55,508 --> 00:59:57,427
