920
01:00:05,476 --> 01:00:07,103
Tapi apa boleh buat?

921
01:00:08,104 --> 01:00:11,149
Dia dah berjumpa Peguam Hong Yu-chan.

922
01:00:11,858 --> 01:00:12,900
Apa?

923
01:00:21,826 --> 01:00:22,827
Ya, En. Yu.

924
01:00:24,078 --> 01:00:24,996
Saya…

925
01:00:27,582 --> 01:00:28,541
